column5: Might be my last bass report for the season.Might.LOL
Couple nice piggies there Brian, but jeeeeeeez, folks say I'M the one that never smiles in fish'n pictures
Some were wondering if we are related too. Morning Lew
hey, shouldn't you photoshop the background so no one knows where you are...LOL  they were nice fish
Nice fish for sure, Brian.  AHHHHHHHH, cottage country...gotta love it.

Hey Brian, Fishing docks and boats Brian??? I never thought of that pattern last weekend..LOL. I'm sure you caught those smallies in another area !!! Nice fish though. Still another month to catch some more Simcoe hogs.....
what no white bucket!  nice fish for sure , beauty day as well . hoping for at least one more bassin trip in 2 weeks.  TB
Darn things are a lot easier to catch when there isn`t a weigh in near by! Nice fish Brian.
Nice fish Brian. Don't they seem more co-operative when you don't have any pressure to bring 'em in?
YES  nice fish brian !!!! and like you said where were they last weekend ???/  LOL..LOL nice pics too...cheers
